Basic bio data on athletes and medal results from Summer Games in Rio 2016.

Source: R/data.R
olympic.Rd

Basic bio data on athletes and medal results from Summer Games in Rio 2016.

olympic

Format

A data frame with 13688 rows and 12 variables:

ID

Unique number for each athlete

Name

Athlete's name

Sex

M or F

Age

Integer in years

Height

In centimeters

Weight

In kilograms

Team

Team name

NOC

National Olympic Committee 3-letter code

Games

Year and season

Sport

Sport

Event

Event

Medal

Gold, Silver, Bronze, or NA

Source

https://www.kaggle.com/heesoo37/olympic-history-data-a-thorough-analysis/data

Examples

plot(dplyr::sample_frac(olympic, 0.05))

summary(olympic)
